    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Although the underlying COU2 assessment concluded Not Accepted due to widespread credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, this UnitOfAssurance package is formally accepted for submission to the evidence repository as a documented negative finding. The package faithfully records all 13 factor assessments, the Monte Carlo UQ results, and the epistemic gaps identified. It is accepted as a complete credibility dossier demonstrating that the model does not yet meet the required credibility levels for Class III VAD regulatory use, and that further validation activities are needed before a positive acceptance decision can be rendered.",
